Now, change it to he.

290
00:11:19,010 --> 00:11:20,400
He plays football.

291
00:11:21,040 --> 00:11:21,400
Excellent.

292
00:11:22,060 --> 00:11:23,060
You are getting it right.

293
00:11:23,885 --> 00:11:25,005
Let's do some more practice.

294
00:11:26,460 --> 00:11:27,740
They study English.

