00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:30,320
They study English.

296
00:11:31,020 --> 00:11:32,020
Now, change it to she.

297
00:11:32,710 --> 00:11:34,460
She studies English.

298
00:11:34,560 --> 00:11:35,560
That's correct.

299
00:11:36,220 --> 00:11:41,560
You see, when the verb ends with Y,
