314
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,420
I go to school.

315
00:12:19,070 --> 00:12:20,080
I go to school.

316
00:12:20,850 --> 00:12:22,140
She goes to school.

317
00:12:22,540 --> 00:12:23,540
