347
00:13:31,570 --> 00:13:34,920
When we say no, we use doesn't.

348
00:13:35,550 --> 00:13:36,820
That means does not.

349
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,480
Yes, sir.

350
00:13:38,520 --> 00:13:39,520
