00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:02,060
I come home at one o'clock.

362
00:14:02,760 --> 00:14:03,760
I eat lunch.

363
00:14:04,620 --> 00:14:05,620
I rest.

364
00:14:05,990 --> 00:14:07,000
I do my homework.

365
00:14:07,900 --> 00:14:08,900
I watch TV.

366
00:14:09,655 --> 00:14:11,380
I go to bed at ten o'clock.

367
00:14:12,220 --> 00:14:13,220
