368
00:14:13,850 --> 00:14:15,200
I get up at seven.

369
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:17,180
I brush my teeth.

370
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:19,020
I take a shower.

371
00:14:19,740 --> 00:14:20,660
I eat breakfast.

372
00:14:20,710 --> 00:14:22,740
I go to school.

373
00:14:23,780 --> 00:14:24,860
I study English.

374
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:27,120
I play with my friends.

375
00:14:27,940 --> 00:14:29,700
I come home at one o'clock.

376
00:14:30,490 --> 00:14:31,490
I eat lunch.

