00:17:19,840 --> 00:17:21,280
Yes, it is okay.

454
00:17:22,190 --> 00:17:24,240
Speaking slowly is good for learning.

455
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,460
You will become faster with time.

456
00:17:27,190 --> 00:17:29,680
Focus on being clear, not fast.

457
00:17:30,260 --> 00:17:31,260
Yes, sir.

458
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:32,220
I will do that.

459
00:17:32,221 --> 00:17:33,221
Good.

460
00:17:33,460 --> 00:17:34,960
Keep using simple sentences.

461
00:17:35,880 --> 00:17:37,180
You can say I walk.

